{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "techx-todo-api-collection",
    "name": "TechX Todo API",
    "description": "Collection para testar a API do desafio TechX To-Do List.\n\n## Setup\n1. Importe esta collection e um environment (local ou production)\n2. Execute **Auth → Get CSRF Token** (salva `csrfToken`)\n3. **Auth → Register** ou **Login** (cookies HttpOnly + `csrfToken` no body)\n4. Requests mutáveis enviam header `X-CSRF-Token`\n5. Postman envia cookies automaticamente (Cookie Jar)\n\nAlternativa: Bearer `{{token}}` ainda funciona para testes manuais.\n\n## Endpoints Auth\n- GET /auth/csrf\n- POST /auth/login, /auth/register\n- GET /auth/me\n- POST /auth/logout",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "csrfToken",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "userId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "taskId",
      "value": "1"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/health",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "health"]
            },
            "description": "Verifica status da API, MySQL e MongoDB."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get CSRF Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('csrfToken', body.csrfToken);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('csrfToken', body.csrfToken);",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Returns csrfToken', () => {",
                  "  pm.expect(pm.response.json().csrfToken).to.be.a('string');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/csrf",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "csrf"]
            },
            "description": "Obtém token CSRF (cookie + variável para header X-CSRF-Token)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('csrfToken', body.csrfToken);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', String(body.user.id));",
                  "  pm.environment.set('csrfToken', body.csrfToken);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('userId', String(body.user.id));",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "pm.test('Returns user and csrfToken', () => {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.expect(body.user).to.be.an('object');",
                  "  pm.expect(body.csrfToken).to.be.a('string');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Matheus Soares\",\n  \"email\": \"matheus@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"123456\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Cadastra um novo usuário. Retorna JWT e dados do usuário (sem senha)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('csrfToken', body.csrfToken);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', String(body.user.id));",
                  "  pm.environment.set('csrfToken', body.csrfToken);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('userId', String(body.user.id));",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Returns user and csrfToken', () => {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.expect(body.user).to.be.an('object');",
                  "  pm.expect(body.csrfToken).to.be.a('string');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"matheus@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"123456\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Autentica usuário existente. Define cookies HttpOnly + csrfToken."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Me",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "me"]
            },
            "description": "Retorna usuário autenticado (requer cookie de sessão)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "X-CSRF-Token",
                "value": "{{csrfToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "logout"]
            },
            "description": "Encerra sessão e limpa cookies."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Register - Validation Error (example)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"A\",\n  \"email\": \"invalid-email\",\n  \"password\": \"123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Exemplo de payload inválido — esperado 400 com details de validação."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Tasks",
      "description": "Endpoints protegidos. Após Login, cookies são enviados automaticamente. Mutações exigem header X-CSRF-Token.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Tasks",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/tasks",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "tasks"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Task",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-CSRF-Token",
                "value": "{{csrfToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"Estudar TypeScript\",\n  \"description\": \"Revisar decorators e DI\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/tasks",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "tasks"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Task by ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "tasks", "{{taskId}}"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Task",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-CSRF-Token",
                "value": "{{csrfToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"Estudar TypeScript (atualizado)\",\n  \"description\": \"Revisar TSyringe e Express\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "tasks", "{{taskId}}"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Toggle Task Completed",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "X-CSRF-Token",
                "value": "{{csrfToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}/toggle",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "tasks", "{{taskId}}", "toggle"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Task",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "X-CSRF-Token",
                "value": "{{csrfToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "tasks", "{{taskId}}"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Task Metadata (MongoDB)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}/metadata",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "tasks", "{{taskId}}", "metadata"]
            },
            "description": "Metadados extras no MongoDB (tags, priority, notes, history)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Upsert Task Metadata (MongoDB)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-CSRF-Token",
                "value": "{{csrfToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"tags\": [\"estudo\", \"backend\"],\n  \"priority\": \"high\",\n  \"notes\": \"Prioridade para o desafio\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}/metadata",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "tasks", "{{taskId}}", "metadata"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
